							<svg role="img" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" title="Python"><path fill="#3776AB" d="M14.25.18l.9.2.73.26.59.3.45.32.34.34.25.34.16.33.1.3.04.26.02.2-.01.13V8.5l-.05.63-.13.55-.21.46-.26.38-.3.31-.33.25-.35.19-.35.14-.33.1-.3.07-.26.04-.21.02H8.77l-.69.05-.59.14-.5.22-.41.27-.33.32-.27.35-.2.36-.15.37-.1.35-.07.32-.04.27-.02.21v3.06H3.17l-.21-.03-.28-.07-.32-.12-.35-.18-.36-.26-.36-.36-.35-.46-.32-.59-.28-.73-.21-.88-.14-1.05L0 11.97l.06-1.22.16-1.04.24-.87.32-.71.36-.57.4-.44.42-.33.42-.24.4-.16.36-.1.32-.05.24-.01h.16l.06.01h8.16v-.83H6.18l-.01-2.75-.02-.37.05-.34.11-.31.17-.28.25-.26.31-.23.38-.2.44-.18.51-.15.58-.12.64-.1.71-.06.77-.04.84-.02 1.27.05 1.07.13zm-6.3 1.98l-.23.33-.08.41.08.41.23.34.33.22.41.09.41-.09.33-.22.23-.34.08-.41-.08-.41-.23-.33-.33-.22-.41-.09-.41.09-.33.22zM21.1 6.11l.28.06.32.12.35.18.36.27.36.35.35.47.32.59.28.73.21.88.14 1.04.05 1.23-.06 1.23-.16 1.04-.24.86-.32.71-.36.57-.4.45-.42.33-.42.24-.4.16-.36.09-.32.05-.24.02-.16-.01h-8.22v.82h5.84l.01 2.76.02.36-.05.34-.11.31-.17.29-.25.25-.31.24-.38.2-.44.17-.51.15-.58.13-.64.09-.71.07-.77.04-.84.01-1.27-.04-1.07-.14-.9-.2-.73-.25-.59-.3-.45-.33-.34-.34-.25-.34-.16-.33-.1-.3-.04-.25-.02-.2.01-.13v-5.34l.05-.64.13-.54.21-.46.26-.38.3-.32.33-.24.35-.2.35-.14.33-.1.3-.06.26-.04.21-.02.13-.01h5.84l.69-.05.59-.14.5-.21.41-.28.33-.32.27-.35.2-.36.15-.36.1-.35.07-.32.04-.28.02-.21V6.07h2.09l.14.04zm-6.47 14.25l-.23.33-.08.41.08.41.23.33.33.23.41.08.41-.08.33-.23.23-.33.08-.41-.08-.41-.23-.33-.33-.23-.41-.08-.41.08-.33.23z"/></svg>
						</div>
					</div>
					<p>Object-document mapper for MongoDB and Redis implemented in Python. Lightweight ODM with custom serialisation and common pattern examples.</p>
					<p class="tech">Python · pymongo · redis-py</p>
				</div>

				<div class="project-card">
					<div class="project-title-row">
						<h3><a href="https://github.com/itzi97/engine2d" target="_blank" rel="noopener">2D Game Engine</a></h3>
						<div class="icons">
							<svg role="img" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" title="C++"><path fill="#00599C" d="M22.394 6c-.167-.29-.398-.543-.652-.69L12.926.22c-.509-.294-1.34-.294-1.848 0L2.26 5.31c-.508.293-.923 1.013-.923 1.6v10.18c0 .294.104.62.271.91.167.29.398.543.652.69l8.816 5.09c.508.293 1.34.293 1.848 0l8.816-5.09c.254-.147.485-.4.652-.69.167-.29.27-.616.27-.91V6.91c.003-.294-.1-.62-.268-.91zM12 19.109c-3.92 0-7.109-3.189-7.109-7.109S8.08 4.891 12 4.891a7.133 7.133 0 0 1 6.156 3.552l-3.076 1.781A3.567 3.567 0 0 0 12 8.445c-1.96 0-3.554 1.595-3.554 3.555S10.04 15.555 12 15.555a3.57 3.57 0 0 0 3.08-1.778l3.077 1.78A7.135 7.135 0 0 1 12 19.109zm7.109-6.714h-.79v.79h-.79v-.79h-.79v-.79h.79v-.79h.79v.79h.79zm2.962 0h-.79v.79h-.79v-.79h-.79v-.79h.79v-.79h.79v.79h.79z"/></svg>
							<svg role="img" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" title="Lua"><path fill="#2C2D72" d="M11.993 0C5.37 0 0 5.373 0 12s5.37 12 11.993 12C18.63 24 24 18.627 24 12S18.63 0 11.993 0zm5.392 5.56a2.19 2.19 0 1 1 0 4.382 2.19 2.19 0 0 1 0-4.381zm-5.42 1.668c2.9 0 5.244 2.126 5.244 4.74 0 2.616-2.345 4.74-5.244 4.74s-5.244-2.124-5.244-4.74c0-2.614 2.346-4.74 5.244-4.74zm0 1.363c-2.147 0-3.886 1.514-3.886 3.378 0 1.865 1.739 3.378 3.886 3.378s3.884-1.513 3.884-3.378c0-1.864-1.737-3.378-3.884-3.378zm2.74 1.463a1.26 1.26 0 1 1 0 2.521 1.26 1.26 0 0 1 0-2.521z"/></svg>
						</div>
					</div>
					<p>Personal ongoing 2D game engine built from scratch with a Lua scripting layer. Demonstrates low-level systems programming and engine architecture outside of coursework.</p>
					<p class="tech">C++ · Lua · Sol2 · SDL3 · GLM · CMake</p>
				</div>
			</section>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>

<style>
	.eyebrow {
		font-family: var(--font-mono);
		color: var(--accent);
		font-size: 0.85rem;
		margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
		margin-top: 0;
	}
	.section-heading {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: space-between;
		align-items: end;
		gap: 1.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
	}
	.section-heading h2 {
		margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
	}
	.section-heading p {
		margin: 0;
		color: var(--text-muted);
		max-width: 40rem;
	}
	.view-all {
		color: var(--accent);
		text-decoration: none;
		font-weight: 600;
		white-space: nowrap;
	}
	.view-all:hover {
		text-decoration: underline;
	}
	.project-title-row {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 0.6em;
		margin-bottom: 0.4em;
	}
	.project-title-row h3 {
		margin: 0;
	}
	.icons {
		display: flex;
		gap: 0.35em;
		align-items: center;
		flex-shrink: 0;
	}
	.icons svg {
		width: 15px;
		height: 15px;
		display: block;
		flex-shrink: 0;
	}
</style>
